metadata.name: Unicult Shadow Edition #1
metadata.description: The story of Unicult dates back to 1938, founded in Scotland, the cult sought to uncover an alternate dimension where they believed eternal life was a possibility. In their efforts to discover immortality, a cult member, nicknamed Dr Bonkers, has built a gateway rumoured to have opened a path to a new realm. Shortly after the alleged discovery of the portal, all so-called Cult Members have mysteriously vanished without a trace… Until now…
